/Lumina_Image_2.0_Repackaged/resolve/main/split_files/vae/ae.safetensors?download=true)  \n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/vae`  \n\n---\n\n## 🆙 Load Upscale Model  \n\n### Download 4x_NMKD-Siax_200k.pth mode from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Akumetsu971/SD_Anime_Futuristic_Armor/resolve/main/4x_NMKD-Siax_200k.pth?download=true)  \n\n**Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/upscale_models`\n\n---\n\n## 🧩 Nodes Installed from Manager  \n\n- **ComfyUI-Easy-Use**\n- **rgthree-comfy**\n- **ComfyUI-Inpaint-CropAndStitch**\n\n---\n\n## 📚 Resources  \n🎥 **Tutorials:** [Pixaroma YouTube Channel](https://www.youtube.com/@pixaroma)  \n💬 **Community Discord:** [Join Here](https://discord.com/invite/gggpkVgBf3)\n\nLearn more about Kontext model on [Comfy.org](https://docs.comfy.org/tutorials/flux/flux-1-kontext-dev) and [blf.ai](https://bfl.ai/models/flux-kontext)\n\nLearn how to prompt for Flux Kontext [HERE](https://docs.bfl.ai/guides/prompting_guide_kontext_i2i) and [HERE](https://docs.comfy.org/tutorials/flux/flux-1-kontext-dev#flux-kontext-prompt-techniques)\n"],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"}],"links":[[7,3,0,8,0,"LATENT"],[26,27,0,8,1,"VAE"],[27,11,0,28,0,"CONDITIONING"],[28,7,0,28,1,"CONDITIONING"],[29,28,0,3,1,"CONDITIONING"],[30,28,1,3,2,"CONDITIONING"],[31,27,0,28,2,"VAE"],[40,28,2,3,3,"LATENT"],[41,30,0,33,0,"IMAGE"],[42,30,1,33,1,"MASK"],[43,33,1,31,0,"IMAGE"],[44,8,0,34,1,"IMAGE"],[45,33,0,34,0,"STITCHER"],[48,33,1,28,3,"IMAGE"],[49,33,2,28,4,"MASK"],[59,34,0,43,0,"*"],[60,43,0,9,0,"IMAGE"],[64,48,0,3,0,"MODEL"],[65,47,0,6,0,"CLIP"],[66,47,0,7,0,"CLIP"],[67,49,0,11,0,"CONDITIONING"],[68,33,1,50,0,"IMAGE"],[69,50,0,49,1,"LATENT"],[70,6,0,49,0,"CONDITIONING"],[71,27,0,50,1,"VAE"]],"groups":[],"config":{},"extra":{"ds":{"scale":0.8140274938684061,"offset":[421.29778510955106,292.19773213224283]},"frontendVersion":"1.23.4","VHS_latentpreview":false,"VHS_latentpreviewrate":0,"VHS_MetadataImage":true,"VHS_KeepIntermediate":true,"ue_links":[]},"version":0.4}